snippet.title: Fire Fighter for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Uhm, a disappointing title by Imagic, who usually make good Atari 2600 games.

Well, it isn't bad, but it's extremly repetitive. Graphically itisn't as good as other Imagic titles either.
